Introduction

Jung Wook Jin, known under his stage name as Nine, is a South Korean K-POP Idol under 8D Entertainment. He is the Maknae and Vocalist of OnlyOneOf, and made his debut on May 28th, 2019 with the mini album "OnlyOneOf yOu'.
